++  scry-succeed
  |=  [date=@da result=cage]  ^-  sley
  |=  [* (unit (set monk)) =term =beam]
  ^-  (unit (unit cage))
  ::
  ~|  scry-succeed+[beam+beam term+term]
  ?>  =(term %cx)
  ?>  =(beam [[~nul %desk %da date] /bar/foo])
  ::
  [~ ~ result]
::  +scry-fail: produces a scry function with a known request and failed answer
